---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Autonomous Mobile Robots — Formic Automate NOW"
  description="AMR fleets that handle pallet and tote movement between dock, staging, line, and outbound, running alongside your team — reducing forklift injuries and product damage without replacing your drivers."
  ogTitle="Autonomous Mobile Robots — Formic"
  ogDescription="AMR fleets for pallet handling. Fully managed under the Formic Full Service model."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/solutions/amrs" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/solutions">Solutions</a><span class="sep">/</span>AMRs
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">AMRs</div>
    <h1>Autonomous Mobile Robots<br><em>for Pallet Handling.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">AMR fleets that handle pallet and tote movement between dock, staging, line, and outbound, running alongside your team, reducing forklift injuries and product damage without replacing your drivers.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/AMR-warehouse.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · AMR fleet</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Why It Matters</div>
      <h2>Forklifts are <em>the silent cost</em>.</h2>
      <p>Forklifts are the highest single-source injury risk on most CPG and warehousing floors, and they damage pallets, racking, and product on routine moves that don't require a human driver at all. Autonomous mobile robots replace those repeating routes, freeing forklift operators for inbound, staging exceptions, and the work that actually requires judgment.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Fewer forklift-related injury claims and less product damage</li>
        <li>Predictable cycle times for line-side replenishment</li>
        <li>No CapEx — 24/7 support and 100% maintenance included</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get a quote →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/AMR-warehouse.jpg" alt="Formic AMR moving a pallet through a warehouse" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Autonomous · pallet handling</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic AMR fleet running in a production facility" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Fleet · scaled deployment</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — How It Works</div>
      <h2>Routes that <em>adapt</em>.</h2>
      <p>SLAM-based navigation means no floor tape, no embedded wires, and no facility modifications required. The fleet maps your floor on deployment and adapts to pallet placement and traffic in real time.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Dynamic routing — adapts to changing floor layouts</li>
        <li>Integrated with WMS, ERP, and MES systems for real-time inventory tracking as AMRs move</li>
        <li>Safe by design — slows and stops around humans automatically</li>
        <li>Mixed traffic with manual forklifts and pedestrians</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Specs</div>
      <h2>Fleets that <em>scale</em>.</h2>
      <p>Start with two AMRs, scale to thirty. Add capacity as your pallet flow grows — same software, same fleet manager, same SLA.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Fleet sizes from 2 to 30+ AMRs</li>
        <li>Payloads: up to 1,500 kg per unit, larger options available</li>
        <li>Pallet compatibility: standard GMA 48×40", custom sizes available on request</li>
        <li>Battery: opportunity charging, no shift-end swaps</li>
        <li>Integration via REST API or message-bus — compatible with major WMS platforms including SAP, Oracle, and Manhattan Associates</li>
        <li>Safety: ANSI/RIA R15.08 mobile robot compliant</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/full-service" class="larr">How Full Service works →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-9787.jpg" alt="AMR fleet operations" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Fleet · WMS-integrated</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:flex-start">What's Included</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4.4vw,64px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.04;color:var(--white);margin:10px 0 14px">One monthly fee. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Everything included.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Fleet scoping and facility mapping</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>AMR hardware and charging infrastructure</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>WMS/ERP integration</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Installation and commissioning</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>24/7 fleet monitoring and support</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>All maintenance and parts</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Performance SLAs</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Fleet expansion under the same agreement</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Move pallets<br><em>without moving people.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/solutions" class="btn-ctawh">All Solutions</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
